{"meta":{"updateDate":1755117017718,"pPcc":"SAT#P","questionId":"50338a48","skill_cd":"P.A.","score_band_range_cd":2,"skill_desc":"Equivalent expressions","createDate":1755117017718,"program":"SAT","primary_class_cd_desc":"Advanced Math","ibn":"","external_id":"56e878c9-7295-480c-8ba1-5c2246df36be","primary_class_cd":"P","uId":"d4bd12a4-d755-4e7a-b314-8dbe51f8ee82","difficulty":"E"},"source":"modern","detail":{"type":"mcq","stem":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Which expression is equivalent to&nbsp;<math alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi></math>?</p>","keys":["2012d255-496b-4b1a-b58b-274465b1ad9f"],"answerOptions":[{"id":"2012d255-496b-4b1a-b58b-274465b1ad9f","content":"<p><math alttext=\"w left parenthesis 15 w plus 8 right parenthesis\"><mi>w</mi><mfenced><mrow><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"4f80c760-51c7-4bce-9439-58b3f95a56e9","content":"<p><math alttext=\"8 w left parenthesis 15 w plus 1 right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi><mfenced><mrow><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"84dc785c-833f-48ff-a78d-c41bb6fedb39","content":"<p><math alttext=\"15 w squared left parenthesis 8 w plus 1 right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mfenced><mrow><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"},{"id":"18e367a3-3168-4a00-b41c-7be9d8d4362b","content":"<p><math alttext=\"23 left parenthesis w squared plus w right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>23</mn></mrow><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>w</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"}],"rationale":"<p>Choice A is correct. Since each term of the given expression has a common factor of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"w\"><mi>w</mi></math>, it may be rewritten as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"w left parenthesis 15 w plus 8 right parenthesis\"><mi>w</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></math>. Therefore, the expression <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"w left parenthesis 15 w plus 8 right parenthesis\"><mi>w</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></math> is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mn>15</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>w</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice B is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"120 w squared plus 8 w\"><mn>120</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>w</mi></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mn>15</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>w</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice C is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"120 w cubed plus 15 w squared\"><mn>120</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>15</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mn>15</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>w</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice D is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"23 w squared plus 23 w\"><mn>23</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>23</mn><mi>w</mi></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"15 w squared plus 8 w\"><mn>15</mn><msup><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>w</mi></math>.</p>","externalid":"56e878c9-7295-480c-8ba1-5c2246df36be","correct_answer":["A"]}}